<br>
 On the other hand I have had success equipping other peoples pets with weapons that were not equipable by my own pet i.e. I have had success equipping enchanter pets with things like beastlord/monk only weaps that I was unable to utilize ( I believe those pets must follow a different guide as to what they can use.)  <br>
<br>
